{
  "stem": "25835.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they let us wait on the open place, which was, unfortunately, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] upper part of crematorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the time, 24 hours daily, they burnt corpses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And smell was unbelievable, so hard to-- even to be there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After a couple days, they took us to one barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They check us-- they count us each day at 5 o'clock in the-- when still was dark each day, and keeping us in Appellplatz for a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One day, I lost strength, and I was falling down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ran very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This SS woman-- you know how they had big, black leather shoes-- and with whip inside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She took this whip, she beat me, and said in nice words, you have to stay, you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then other women, they tried to keep me for counting, from other-- each place taking with finger because I-- I-- I was too, too weak.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Thank God, after a couple days, they took us to Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somebody thought that this transportation of women-- this was only for women, Ravensbruck-- it will be-- is, is going to ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Everybody has to strip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember cold, because it was autumn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in the middle was sitting on the chair, a couple civilian men and couple SS man, SS man officers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they, they let us go around in circle, naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Again, shock for me to be with old women, with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a different time, not, not like now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother was, for me, always very elegant, very clean, very nice person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later, I saw her naked-- shocked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many women wounded or with some diseases.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was also terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
